subvgradeDF = spark.read.load('abfss://datalake@dus02store.dfs.core.windows.net/fromAtlas/submissionvgrades.json', format='json')

subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Assessment Name', 'AssessmentName')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Course ID', 'CourseID')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Subject Area', 'SubjectArea')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Catalog Number', 'CatalogNumber')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Course Name', 'CourseName')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumnRenamed('Term Code', 'TermCode')
subvgradeDF = subvgradeDF.withColumn("DueTime", to_timestamp(col("Student's Due Date"), "dd/MM/yyyy HH:mm"))

AssignmentDF = AssignmentDF.join(subvgradeDF, ['AssessmentName', 'CourseID', 'SubjectArea', 'CatalogNumber', 'CourseName', 'TermCode', 'Year'])\
                            .select('AssessmentName', 'CourseID', 'SubjectArea', 'CatalogNumber', 'CourseName', 'TermCode', 'Year',
                                    AssignmentDF.InitialDueTime, AssignmentDF.GlobalExtensionDueTime, AssignmentDF.InitialDueDateSK,
                                    AssignmentDF.GlobalExtensionDueSK, AssignmentDF.AssignmentSK, AssignmentDF.DueTime, 
                                    subvgradeDF.DueTimeAltered)
